- Defines funcs from `syscall/js` package from JS side

  // func valueGet(v ref, p string) ref
  "syscall/js.valueGet": (sp) => {
    storeValue(sp + 32, Reflect.get(loadValue(sp + 8), loadString(sp + 16)));
