* Reactive framework

- Markup format/DSL
- State managment
- Create a component
- Attach component to DOM tree

: moving pieces of a framework
: Markup format/DSL = how elements will be configured
: State managment = how are we going to handle state (global/local/properties)
: Create a component = configure properties + event handlers + attaching component to state manager
: Attach component to dom = start rendering loop, generate virtual dom, diff virtual dom to generate changes and apply changes to real dom tree
: idea of framework like that is to minimize amount of interactions that will happen with dom in the browser

